com.sterlingcommerce.ui.web.framework.helpers

Class SCUIStateHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sterlingcommerce.ui.web.framework.helpers.SCUIStateHelper

  • public class SCUIStateHelper
extends java.lang.Object
    Helper class which can be invoked by applications to easily save/retrieve state information.
    The helper class turns around and calls the plugged in ISCUIStateProvider class statikonda ISCUIStateProvider
